      • getIgnoreNull

        boolean getIgnoreNull()
         Optional. Rows with `null` values will automatically fail a rule, unless
 `ignore_null` is `true`. In that case, such `null` rows are trivially
 considered passing.

 Only applicable to ColumnMap rules.
